      "id": 3780,
      "category": "team",
      "content": "A remote code execution (RCE) vulnerability was found on a DoD website which could have enabled an attacker to execute remote commands on the web server. @joaomatosf, was able to demonstrate this vulnerability by developing a custom script that caused the webserver to execute a benign command. This was a very clever demonstration. Thanks @joaomatosf, and well done!",
